com.netflix.spectator.atlas.impl

Interface Query

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Query.And, Query.Equal, Query.GreaterThan, Query.GreaterThanEqual, Query.Has, Query.In, Query.LessThan, Query.LessThanEqual, Query.Not, Query.Or, Query.Regex

    public interface Query
    Query for matching based on tags. For more information see: https://github.com/Netflix/atlas/wiki/Stack-Language#query Classes in this package are only intended for use internally within spectator. They may change at any time and without notice.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  Query.And
      Query that matches if both sub-queries match.
      static class  Query.Equal
      Query that matches if the tag map contains key k with value v.
      static class  Query.GreaterThan
      Query that matches if the tag map contains key k with a value that is lexically greater than v.
      static class  Query.GreaterThanEqual
      Query that matches if the tag map contains key k with a value that is lexically greater than or equal to v.
      static class  Query.Has
      Query that matches if the tag map contains a specified key.
      static class  Query.In
      Query that matches if the tag map contains key k with a value in the set vs.
      static class  Query.LessThan
      Query that matches if the tag map contains key k with a value that is lexically less than v.
      static class  Query.LessThanEqual
      Query that matches if the tag map contains key k with a value that is lexically less than or equal to v.
      static class  Query.Not
      Query that matches if the sub-query does not match.
      static class  Query.Or
      Query that matches if either sub-queries match.
      static class  Query.Regex
      Query that matches if the tag map contains key k with a value that matches the regex in v.

      • matches

        boolean matches(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> tags)
        Check to see if this query matches a set of tags. Common tags or changes to fix invalid characters should be performed prior to checking for a match.
        Parameters:
        tags - Tags to use when checking for a match.
        Returns:
        True if the query expression matches the tag map.

      • matches

        default boolean matches(com.netflix.spectator.api.Id id)
        Check to see if this query matches an id. Equivalent to calling matches(Map) with the result of toMap(Id).
        Parameters:
        id - Id to use when checking for a match.
        Returns:
        True if the query expression matches the id.

      • exactTags

        default java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> exactTags()
        Extract the tags from the query that have an exact match for a given value. That is are specified using an Query.Equal clause.
        Returns:
        Tags that are exactly matched as part of the query.
